Create long-form content outline in markdown [TARGETLANGUAGE]. The content outline should include a minimum of 20 headings and subheadings. The outline should be extensive and cover the whole topic. Use fully detailed subheadings that engage the reader. The outline should also have a conclusion followed by a list of FAQs relevant to the topic. Please provide a catchy title for the article. Also provide an SEO title for the article. Don't write the article, only the outline for writers. The topic of the article is: [KEYWORD]

On the last, write: Please visit my blog: https://www.mangaip.com

Use Tone Friendly, Writing Style Creative

[PROMPT]
title: Best Outline For Blog V 1.0.0
